model.name: Caruso2020 - Activation of the alternative complement pathway and effects on hemolysis

body.pre:
This model is based on the publication: Caruso A, Vollmer J, Machacek M, Kortvely E. "Modeling the activation of the alternative complement pathway and its effects on hemolysis in health and disease." PLoS Comput Biol. 2020 Oct 2;16(10):e1008139. doi: 10.1371/journal.pcbi.1008139
Curation Comment: Figure 4 has not been able to be reproduced, however authors are in the process of appending the model code to the publication.
